quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,Iki n’igisomwa twamanuye nukugitegeka hamwe nukumanura murico aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu ari k’umugaragaro kugira ngo mwibuke
  24,2,"Umushurashuzi kazi hamwe n’umu shurashuzi nimubakubite umwe wese inkoni\tijana\t(100),\tkandi\tntimubagirire\tikigongwe\tkw’itegeko\try’Imana, nimwaba mwemera Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka, kandi habe n’ivyabona vy’ibihano vyabo hamwe n’umurwi waba Isilamu"
  24,3,"Umushurashuzi ntahuza igitsina ciwe atari k’umushurashuzi kazi nkawe canke kumugore agereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, n’umushurashuzi kazi ntahuza igitsina ciwe atari kumu shurashuzi canke kumugabo agereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, ivyo vyose bikaba bibujijwe kuba Isilamu bose"
  24,4,"Nabamwe babeshera abagore bisukuye neza hanyuma ntibazane ivyabona vy’abantu bane, abo bantu nibakubitwe inkoni mirongo umunani (80) kandi ntimubemerere ivyabona vyabo kuko abo bantu nibo bononyi"
  24,5,"Dukuyemwo bamwe basaba ikigongwe munyuma yivyo vyose nugutegura ibikorwa vyiza, ntankeka Imana niyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’Impuhwe zihagije"
  24,6,"Nabamwe babeshera abakenyezi babo atavyabona bafise ataribo bonyene kubwabo, rero ukuba icabona c’umwe umwe muribo kuzoba ari ukurahira kw’incuro\tzine\tkundahiro\ty’Imana\tatankeka\tyuko\tari\tumwe\twabavugisha ukuri kwama"
  24,7,Nubugira gatanu nukurahira yuko umuvumo w’Imana ube kuriwe niyaba ari mubantu b’ababeshi
  24,8,"Ivyo\tbihano\tbizomuvako\tyiyemeje\tmu\tkwemanga\tarahiye\tincuro\tzine zijanye n’indahiro y’Imana yuko ari umwe mubabeshi"
  24,9,"Nubugira\tgatanu\tnuko\tishavu\try’Imana\triba\tkuriwe\tniyaba\tari\tmuba vugisha ukuri"
  24,10,"Iyo hataba\timigisha\ty’Imana\tkuri\tmwebwe\tn’Impuhwe\tzayo,\tnukuba Imana ariyo yakira imbabazi z’abantu n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  24,11,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe mubazanye ubwo bubeshi n’umurwi womuri mwebwe nyene, rero ntimwiyumvire yuko ari ishari kuri mwebwe ahubwo n’amahoro, umuntu uwariwe wese muribo azoronswa ico yasoromye kiri muri ivyo bicumuro, nuwikoreye bimwe muri ivyo azoronka ibihano bininiya cane"
  24,12,"Mbega mugihe mwumva izi nkuru, aba Isilamu hamwe naba Isilamu kazi ntibiketse bagenzi babo ineza nukuvuga bati:- ibi nivyiyadukije biri k’umugaragaro"
  24,13,"Mbega ko batazanye ivyabona vy’abantu bane, mugihe babura ivyo vyabona niho imbere y’Imana bazoba ari ababeshi nyakuri"
  24,14,"Iyo hataba hejuru yanyu ingabirano y’Imana hamwe n’impuhwe zayo kuri mwebwe ngaha kw’Isi, no mw’Ijuru, ntankeka mwari gushikirwa n’ibihano bininiya"
  24,15,"Mugihe mwabwakira ubwo bubeshi kundimi zanyu muca muvuga mukoresheje iminwa yanyu namwe atavyo muzi, muca mwiyumvira yuko ari ijambo ritoyi mugabo imbere y’Imana ari rininiya cane"
  24,16,"Mbega mugihe mwumva ayo majambo ko mutavuze muti:-ntaruhusha dufise rwukuvuga ibi bintu, ininahazwa niryawe wewe Muremyi wacu ubu n’ububeshi buhanitse"
  24,17,Imana irabahanura mukuda subira kugira akarorero nkaka ni mwaba muri aba Isilamu bukuri
  24,18,"N’Imana irabi garagaza mumajambo yayo matagatifu, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  24,19,"Mu vy‘ukuri bamwe bashaka yuko hasasagara amabi kubemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri, bamenye yuko bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane ngaha kw’Isi no mw’Ijuru, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi namwe ntavyo muzi"
  24,20,Iyo hataba ingabirano y’Imana kuri mwebwe hamwe n’Impuhwe zayo nukuba ariyo ihumuye nukuba ariyo nyene ikigongwe